translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,7,"Kungathini na ukuba kubekho umnqophiso kuAllâh noMthunywa waKhe wabakhonzi bezithixo ngaphandle kwabo nenza umnqophiso nabo ngaseMasjid eNgcwele (eMakkah) oko nje besanyanisekile kuni, yimani ninyaniseke nani kubo. Inene uAllâh Uyabathanda abanyulu"
  9,8,"Ungabakho njani (umnqophiso phakathi kwenu nabo) njengokuba besithi xa benongamele bangazikhathaleli izibophelelo nokuba zezokuzalana nokuba zezomnqophiso na nani? Bayanivuyisa ngamazwi amnandi aphuma emilonyeni yabo kodwa ezintliziyweni zabo bachasene nani, kananjalo uninzi lwabo ngabenzi bokungcola"
  9,9,"Bona bathenge inzuzwana encinane ngeeVesi zika-Allâh, bathintela abantu bangangeni eNdleleni yaKhe; inene kungcolile oko bakwenzayo"
  9,10,"Ngokumayela (nomntu) olikholwa, abawahloniphi amaqhina okuzalana (naye) nawomnqophiso na kakade! Ngabo kanye abangabagabadeli"
  9,11,"Kodwa ukuba bayaguquka, benze iSalâh, banikele ngeZakâh bangabazalwana benu ke ngokwenkolo. Sizicacisa (ngolo hlobo ke iiVesi, Sinike) ingcombolo kubantu abanolwazi"
  9,12,"Ke kaloku ukuba bayazijikela izifungo zabo emva komnqophiso wabo, baze bahlasele inkolo yenu ngokungayamkeli nangokuyigxeka, balweni ke ngoko (abo) baziinkokeli zokungakholwa kuba kakade izifungo zabo azinto yanto kubo khon’ukuze baziyeke (izenzo zokungcola)"
  9,13,"Aniyi kulwa na nabantu abaphule izifungo zabo abade bazama nokugxotha uMthunywa, ekubeni ingabo abaqala ngokuhlasela nina kuqala. Niyaboyika na? UAllâh Unelungelo elingaphaya lokuba noyike Yena ukuba ningamakholwa"